54.4	Hellraiser	Hellraiser	Hellraiser (also known as Clive Barker's Hellraiser) is a 1987 British horror film based upon the novella The Hellbound Heart by Clive Barker, who also wrote the screenplay and directed the film. The film spawned a series of sequels. A remake was announced and might be presented in 3D. Hellraiser was number 19 on the cable channel Bravo's list of the 100 Scariest Movie Moments.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c4/Hellraiser_poster.png/215px-Hellraiser_poster.png
